// TryOptimizeHuffmanForRle additionally needs fresh litlens/dists with the
// DEFLATE bounds; ZopfliCalculateBitLengths / PatchDistanceCodesForBuggyDecoders

// DEFLATE bounds; ZopfliCalculateBitLengths / PatchDistanceCodesForBuggyDecoders
